Adthena Population Application

1. Run
    a) Requirements:
    - java 1.8 (there must be set path to "java" command in PATH system variable)
    - mongo db is running on localhost on standard port 27017 (I used version 2.6.1)

    b) run script "./run.sh" or "java -jar target/population-1.0.jar"

2. Build
    a) Requirements:
    - java 1.8 (there must be set JAVA_HOME system variable)
    - maven version 3 (I used version 3.0.4, there must be set path to "mvn" command in PATH system variable)

    b) compile, test and build new package "mvn clean package"